          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1692086138860-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Grate your <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1692086141241-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1692086141241-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1692086141241-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1692086141241-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1692086141241-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained wholewheat tortiglioni</strong> to the sauce with most of the <strong>chopped parsley</strong> (save some for garnish!) and mix it all up</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>pasta mixture</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong>, then top with the <strong>grated cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>remaining pasta mixture</strong> and <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and put the dish in the oven for 10-15 min or until all the cheese has melted and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your<strong> chicken breast & cheese veg-packed pasta bake</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1692086143804-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1692086143804-x400.jpg",
