            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> chicken breast & cheese veg-packed pasta</strong> <strong>bake</strong> topped with the <strong>reserved chopped parsley</strong> and a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Loved this recipe? Us too! That’s why it’s one of our Everyday Favourites, available every week.</span></strong></p>",
      "order": 8,
